title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Poparazzi
description:
A lively rockered performer for women who want a board that delivers real all-mountain fun - cruise the groomers, lap the park, explore the trees. The highly approachable Poparazzi is all about value and independence in the face of preconceptions.
To learn more about the Poparazzi visit: arborcollective.com/snowboards/products/poparazzi/
